; For the purpose of this question, the "top three candidates" refers to the candidates with the three highest vote counts in each election; 
; Voter turnout percentage is an indicator of the level of participation in an election, calculated as the number of votes cast divided by the total number of eligible voters, expressed as a percentage;
; This question aims to provide insight into election outcomes and voter engagement.

sql:
SELECT age, gender
FROM voters
ORDER BY age DESC;
